<h2 class="bold font-l">Contrivium</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
JP's version of the trope: a miracle substance that can do anything. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Green Rock</span> </h3>
